"      <a class=\"drug drug_general\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?2/41/2714?source=see_link\">",
"       doxycycline",
"      </a>",
"      (",
"      <a class=\"grade\" href=\"._grade_6?title=Grade 2C\">",
"       Grade 2C",
"      </a>",
"      ). (See",
"      <a class=\"local\" href=\"#H1714648296\">",
"       'Ureaplasma spp'",
"      </a>",
"      above.)",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      For neonates with disease caused by Ureaplasma spp, we suggest",
"      <a class=\"drug drug_general\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?32/43/33456?source=see_link\">",
"       azithromycin",
"      </a>",
"      or",
"      <a class=\"drug drug_general\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?9/57/10138?source=see_link\">",
"       clarithromycin",
"      </a>",
"      (",
"      <a class=\"grade\" href=\"._grade_6?title=Grade 2C\">",
"       Grade 2C",
"      </a>",
"      ). (See",
"      <a class=\"local\" href=\"#H1714648296\">",
